title: Welcome to ELO Hell!!! Playthrough Episode 2

embed.description: Welcome to episode 2 of my new commentary full play series for my adventure through the lands of Silver and hopefully into Gold. Watch me play through, hopefully rage in the future, and maybe pick up some good tips on how I see the game map.

body: I'm stuck in silver, so let's embrace the hate and play it as it is.  Like a spear tote'ing DEMON!!!
